nodes.name: 2'-deoxyuridine 5'-diphosphate:oxidized-thioredoxin 2'-oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: dUDP + Thioredoxin disulfide + H2O <=> Thioredoxin + UDP

nodes.name: 5,10-methylenetetrahydrofolate,NADPH:dUMP C-methyltransferase
nodes.rxn: 5,10-Methylenetetrahydrofolate + dUMP + NADPH + H+ <=> Tetrahydrofolate + dTMP + NADP+

nodes.name: HCO3-:L-glutamine amido-ligase (ADP-forming, carbamate-phosphorylating)
nodes.rxn: 2 ATP + L-Glutamine + HCO3- + H2O <=> 2 ADP + Orthophosphate + L-Glutamate + Carbamoyl phosphate

nodes.name: UTP:ammonia ligase (ADP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + UTP + Ammonia <=> ADP + Orthophosphate + CTP

nodes.name: 2'-deoxyuridine 5'-triphosphate:oxydized-thioredoxin 2'-oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: dUTP + Thioredoxin disulfide + H2O <=> UTP + Thioredoxin

nodes.name: 2'-deoxyuridine 5'-triphosphate:oxydized-thioredoxin 2'-oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: dCTP + Thioredoxin disulfide + H2O <=> CTP + Thioredoxin

nodes.name: 2'-deoxycytidine diphosphate:oxidized-thioredoxin 2'-oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: dCDP + Thioredoxin disulfide + H2O <=> Thioredoxin + CDP

nodes.name: uracil,FMNH2:oxygen oxidoreductase (uracil hydroxylating, ring-opening)
nodes.rxn: Uracil + Reduced FMN + Oxygen <=> (Z)-3-Ureidoacrylate peracid + FMN
